Package: SBRUV
Date: 2026-06-30
Title: Stereo Camera Calibration and Reconstruction for StereoBRUV Practical
Description: Tools for stereo camera calibration and
    3D reconstruction in StereoBRUV applications. It is based on the
    StereoMorph package, with bug fixes, performance improvements, and
    additional convenience functions. The original functionality was
    developed in the StereoMorph package by Aaron Olsen.
Version: 1.1.0
Depends: R (>= 2.11.0)
Imports: grDevices, graphics, stats, utils, bezier (>= 1.1), grid, rjson, shiny (>= 0.13.0), Rcpp (>= 0.9.9), jpeg, tiff, png, svgViewR (>= 1.0.1), MASS
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: rgl
Author: Aaron Olsen, Annat Haber, Jan Jaap Poos
Maintainer: Jan Jaap Poos <janjaap.poos@gmail.com>
